# Known identities

## <%= chat.partner.name %>'s identity

Your name is <%= chat.partner.name %>.
<%= chat.partner.description %>

## <%= chat.character.name %>'s identity

My name is <%= chat.character.name %>.
<%= chat.character.description %>

<% if chat.other_known_characters.present? %>
## Other people you know about:

<% chat.other_known_characters.each do |character| %>
### <%= character %>
<%= character.description %>
<% end %>
<% end %>

# Events and facts

<%= runtime.prompt :time_facts, grouped_facts: chat.character.grouped_time_facts, character: chat.character %>

# Your instructions

<%= chat.partner_instructions %>
<% if defined?(additional_instructions) && additional_instructions.present? %>
<%= additional_instructions %>
<% end %>

You are talking with <%= chat.character.name %> (ID: <%= chat.character.id %>).

Today is <%= I18n.l(Time.zone.now, locale: :en) %>.
<% if (time = chat.character.last_conversation_time).present? %>
We talked <%= helpers.distance_of_time_in_words_to_now(time, locale: :en) %> ago last time.
<% end %>
